Grammar

    0 $accept: program "end file"

    1 program: constdecls forstatement

    2 constdecls: constdecls constdecl
    3           | ε

    4 constdecl: type id ASSIGN intlit SEMICOL
    5          | NOPT type id ASSIGN intlit SEMICOL
    6          | type id ASSIGN LCURLY intlist RCURLY SEMICOL

    7 intlist: intlit COMMA intlist
    8        | intlit
    9        | ε

   10 forstatement: FOR LPAREN constdecl expr SEMICOL unarystmt RPAREN LCURLY forstatement RCURLY
   11             | FOR LPAREN constdecl expr SEMICOL unarystmt RPAREN LCURLY innernest RCURLY

   12 outstatements: outstatements outstatement
   13              | outstatement

   14 innernest: outstatements
   15          | ifstatement
   16          | switchstatement

   17 ifstatement: IF LPAREN ISEVEN id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   18            | IF LPAREN id LESS id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   19            | IF LPAREN id LESSEQUAL id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   20            | IF LPAREN id GREATER id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   21            | IF LPAREN id GREATEREQUAL id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   22            | IF LPAREN ISEDGE id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   23            | IF LPAREN ISEDGE id OR ISEDGE id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY
   24            | IF LPAREN ISEDGE id AND ISEDGE id RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY ELSE LCURLY outstatements RCURLY

   25 switchstatement: SWITCH LPAREN id RPAREN LCURLY casestatements RCURLY

   26 casestatements: casestatement casestatements
   27               | casestatement

   28 casestatement: CASE COLON outstatements

   29 outstatement: OUT ASSIGN expr SEMICOL

   30 type: INT

   31 expr: expr CROSS expr
   32     | expr LESS expr
   33     | expr STAR expr
   34     | expr MINUS expr
   35     | term

   36 unarystmt: loc POSTINC

   37 term: factor
   38     | LPAREN expr RPAREN

   39 factor: intlit
   40       | loc

   41 intlit: INTLITERAL

   42 loc: id
   43    | id LBRACKET id RBRACKET

   44 id: ID


